      "title": "Parliament meets",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Parliament met today for the debate on the adjournment of the Parliament requested by the opposition regarding the increased electricity bills.",
        "A.M. The debate is scheduled to be held from 9.30 am to 4.30 pm.",
        "After that, Parliament will be adjourned until tomorrow and at 1.00 pm tomorrow, President Ranil Wickramasinghe as the Minister of Finance is scheduled to present the interim budget."
      ],
